---
const releaseVersion = '0.1.0';
const downloadUrl = `https://github.com/XiaoXianThis/Origami/releases/download/v${releaseVersion}/Origami-v${releaseVersion}-macos-universal.zip`;
const releaseUrl = `https://github.com/XiaoXianThis/Origami/releases/tag/v${releaseVersion}`;

const installSteps = [
  {
    title: '下载并解压',
    detail: '从 GitHub Releases 下载 zip，解压后将 Origami.app 拖入「应用程序」文件夹。',
  },
  {
    title: '首次打开',
    detail: '未公证的应用需右键 Origami.app →「打开」→ 再点「打开」。或在系统设置 → 隐私与安全性 中允许。',
  },
  {
    title: '授权辅助功能',
    detail: '系统设置 → 隐私与安全性 → 辅助功能 → 勾选 Origami。首次启动时也会弹出系统提示。',
  },
  {
    title: '授权输入监控（可选）',
    detail: '若使用全局快捷键，需在 隐私与安全性 → 输入监控 中勾选 Origami。',
  },
];

const usageSteps = [
  '启动 Origami 后，它会常驻菜单栏',
  '点击菜单栏图标 →「显示窗口」打开设置',
  '将窗口拖入同一组，或通过标签栏操作合并 / 切换',
  '在设置中选择隐藏方式、标签位置等偏好',
];
---

<section id="download" class="border-t border-white/5 px-6 py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-amber-300/80">Download</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white md:text-4xl">下载即用</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-stone-400">
          预构建 Universal 包，Apple Silicon 与 Intel Mac 均可使用。无需 Apple 开发者账号，下载后授权即可运行。
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <a
            href={downloadUrl}
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-300 to-orange-400 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-stone-900 shadow-lg shadow-amber-500/25 transition hover:brightness-110"
          >
            下载 v{releaseVersion}
          </a>
          <a
            href={releaseUrl}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/10 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-stone-200 transition hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/5"
          >
            所有版本
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-stone-500">
          系统要求：macOS 13 Ventura 或更高版本
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/10 bg-[#171923] p-6 shadow-2xl shadow-black/30">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-300">安装步骤</h3>
        <ol class="mt-6 space-y-5">
          {installSteps.map((step, index) => (
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-amber-400/15 text-sm font-semibold text-amber-200">
                {index + 1}
              </span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-stone-200">{step.title}</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-stone-500">{step.detail}</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="getting-started" class="border-t border-white/5 px-6 py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-amber-300/80">Getting Started</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white md:text-4xl">几分钟即可上手</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-stone-400">
          下载预构建包即可使用，也支持从源码构建。Apple Silicon 与 Intel Mac 均可。
        </p>

        <ol class="mt-8 space-y-4">
          {usageSteps.map((step, index) => (
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-amber-400/15 text-sm font-semibold text-amber-200">
                {index + 1}
              </span>
              <span class="pt-1 text-stone-300">{step}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/10 bg-[#171923] p-6 shadow-2xl shadow-black/30">
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-center justify-between">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-300">从源码构建</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-white/5 px-2 py-1 text-xs text-stone-500">bash</span>
        </div>
        <pre class="overflow-x-auto rounded-2xl bg-black/40 p-5 text-sm leading-7 text-stone-300"><code>{`git clone https://github.com/XiaoXianThis/Origami.git
cd Origami
./scripts/package.sh 0.1.0
open dist/Origami.app`}</code></pre>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-stone-500">
          调试构建可使用 <code class="rounded bg-white/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-stone-300">swift build</code>，产物位于
          <code class="rounded bg-white/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-stone-300">.build/debug/Origami</code>。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="border-t border-white/5 px-6 py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl rounded-[2rem] border border-amber-400/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400/10 via-[#171923] to-orange-500/10 px-8 py-12 text-center md:px-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">把散落的窗口，折成整齐的一组</h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-stone-400">
      Origami 为重度多窗口用户设计——写代码、查资料、对文档，标签一切换，思路不中断。
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        href={downloadUrl}
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-stone-900 transition hover:bg-amber-50"
      >
        下载 Origami
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/XiaoXianThis/Origami"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/10 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-stone-200 transition hover:bg-white/5"
      >
        Star on GitHub
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
